   {
      "body" : "Just tested on OSX 10.10 and Ubuntu Linux 14.04.\r\nGenerally it works.\r\nBut IMO it's not worth having a \"window\" menu with one menu item (minimize). Users can use the minimize-window-icon (i guess this is available on windows too) or even use the Dock/Tray-Context-Menu.\r\n\r\nI see no need for this feature.",
      "created_at" : "2014-12-04T20:20:02Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/5424#issuecomment-65696569",
      "id" : 65696569,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/5424",
      "updated_at" : "2014-12-04T20:20:02Z",
      "url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/comments/65696569",
      "user" : {
