   {
      "body" : "While being able to use Command+M to minimize the window is handy, I somewhat agree with @jonasschnelli about adding the window menu item just for minimize. \r\n\r\nWhy not add the 'Bring All to Front' and 'Zoom' items as part of this pull? I was also going to make the accessibility point, but it looks like you bought it up.",
