   {
      "body" : "Would it be possible to support the cmd-key shortcut without the menu? Have a look at the debugwindow code. There is also a key press handling implemented (ESC).\r\n\r\nIMO: OSX Users tend to use \"mission control\", \"hot corners\" and other window zooming/shuffling concepts rather than minimizing every single window.\r\n\r\nACK on a shortcut-only-solution\r\nNACK on a single item menu",
